<p>I'm trying to convert an SVG image to a PNG, but I'm getting the error <code>no decode delegate for this image format ' @ error/blob.c/BlobToImage/364</code>. I'm using the following code - is there something obvious that I've missed out?</p>  <pre><code>$imagick = new imagick(); $imagick-&gt;readImageBlob($this-&gt;render()); $imagick-&gt;setImageFormat("png24"); header("Content-type: image/png"); echo $imagick-&gt;getImageBlob(); </code></pre>  <p>You may notice that I'm passing the <code>render()</code> method - which returns the SVG string - into the <code>readImageBlob()</code> method. </p>